Value HOST (\S+)
Value VRF (\S+)
Value VERSION (\S+)
Value AUTH (auth\s+|noauth\s+|priv\s+)
Value COMMUNITY_STRING ((?:\S+))
Value SOURCE_INTERFACE (\S+)

Start  
  ^snmp-server\s+trap-source\s+(?:${SOURCE_INTERFACE})?\s*$$
  ^snmp-server\s+host\s+(?:${HOST})?(?:\s+vrf\s+${VRF})?(?:\s+version\s+${VERSION})?(?:\s+(?:${AUTH})?(?:${COMMUNITY_STRING}))?\s*$$